      "description": "This system projects an academic, almost clinical, aesthetic through a severely limited palette of desaturated off-whites and dark grays, creating an atmosphere of focused utilitarianism. The meticulous use of varying gray tones defines clear information hierarchy and interaction states without relying on strong color accents. Sharp corners mix with extreme pill-shaped elements, establishing a visual tension between precise structure and approachable interaction, characteristic of AI tools balancing complexity with user-friendliness.",
