      "elevationPhilosophy": "This design systematically avoids strong shadows or complex elevation schemes. Instead, surface differentiation and hierarchy are established primarily through subtle color variations between closely related neutrals (Paper White, Parchment, Graphite). This approach maintains a flat, precise, and understated aesthetic, focusing user attention on content and interaction logic rather than visual depth effects."
